asset.title: VONZIPPER SUPPORT WILDLIFE TOUR – TRAILER 2
asset.description: We hopped back in the van and headed to the mountains again... This time the Support Wildlife Tour got weird in the Rockies with Brendan Gerard, Red Gerard, Blake Axelson, Brian Skorupski, and Chris Frost. The party started and ended in the streets with a few laps through the park at Brighton in-between. Follow the tour socially @vonzipper and #VZWildlifeTour for updates from the van. See you on the road!
asset.author: VonZipper
